26
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:04,740
Do you?

27
00:01:04,740 --> 00:01:05,740
No.

28
00:01:07,910 --> 00:01:11,970
Wait, she called her cell phone with my phone because she couldn't find hers.

29
00:01:11,970 --> 00:01:13,030
Really?

30
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:16,910
I found it!

31
00:01:21,980 --> 00:01:22,910
Is it me?

32
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:24,800
No.

33
00:01:24,980 --> 00:01:26,710
