274
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:03,770
I texted Tae-Ran,
but I heard nothing from her.

275
00:19:03,770 --> 00:19:05,730
Help me meet up with her.

276
00:19:05,730 --> 00:19:07,710
Hey, I was going to ask him that!

277
00:19:07,710 --> 00:19:09,060
Don't take her from me.

278
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:11,870
I'm not kidding.

279
00:19:11,870 --> 00:19:15,910
I felt a connection with Tae-Ran
when we played poker.

280
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:18,660
Yeah right.

281
00:19:18,670 --> 00:19:21,060
Did you see how much Tae-Ran
laughed whenever I made a joke?

282
00:19:24,730 --> 00:19:25,750
