283
00:19:26,750 --> 00:19:30,870
My father taught me to enjoy my life.

284
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:33,130
Let's start enjoying our lives.

285
00:20:15,850 --> 00:20:16,660
Mr. Yeom!

286
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:17,840
