342
00:24:59,810 --> 00:25:02,090
I'll go and get coffee!

343
00:25:09,110 --> 00:25:10,730
Tae-Ran...

344
00:25:14,740 --> 00:25:16,900
We drank a lot last night.

345
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:21,910
