in about 10 years.

346
00:25:22,990 --> 00:25:26,090
I must've been a handful.

347
00:25:26,100 --> 00:25:27,670
Thanks.

348
00:25:30,070 --> 00:25:31,790
Were you that drunk?

349
00:25:33,020 --> 00:25:34,060
You don't remember anything?

350
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:39,970
I was really drunk.

351
00:25:40,690 --> 00:25:42,060
You were drunk too.

352
00:25:44,890 --> 00:25:46,920
We were drunk!

353
00:25:46,940 --> 00:25:48,890
We were both drunk!

354
00:25:48,890 --> 00:25:50,140
We were really drunk!

355
00:25:51,690 --> 00:25:52,740
I wasn't drunk.

356
00:25:55,700 --> 00:25:56,870
I remember everything.

357
00:25:58,060 --> 00:26:01,130
Actually, I enjoyed it.

358
00:26:06,890 --> 00:26:08,660
Yes!

359
00:26:08,660 --> 00:26:09,890
I'm back!

360
00:26:24,830 --> 00:26:29,150
Do you remember
Myung-Pil's friend Ji-Hoon?

361
00:26:31,080 --> 00:26:37,780
He's moving into a huge
apartment in a rich neighborhood.

362
00:26:40,120 --> 00:26:51,840
He never beat Myung-Pil in anything, except for marrying into a rich family.

363
00:26:54,710 --> 00:26:58,860
