if he hears that Ji-Hoon bought a home.

364
00:26:58,860 --> 00:27:01,780
Don't tell him.

365
00:27:04,810 --> 00:27:07,850
Excuse me, can you
drop me off over there?

366
00:27:14,770 --> 00:27:15,750
Why?

367
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:19,150
Why don't we go out for dinner tonight?

368
00:27:19,150 --> 00:27:20,980
I'll tell Myung-Pil to come home early.

369
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:23,690
Why?

370
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:27,890
You had a tough day yesterday
because of the house.

371
00:27:27,890 --> 00:27:32,910
I'm not okay with it either,
but we have no choice.

372
00:27:32,910 --> 00:27:35,710
We have to start working hard again.

373
00:27:35,710 --> 00:27:36,120
So...

374
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:39,660
Okay.

375
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:41,690
Go home.

376
00:27:41,690 --> 00:27:43,090
Bye!

377
00:27:43,090 --> 00:27:45,700
Don't tell him.

378
00:27:52,110 --> 00:27:53,760
It's me, Tae-Ran.

379
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:56,020
Where are you?

380
00:27:58,010 --> 00:28:01,880
I don't have anywhere else
to go but my workroom.

381
00:28:03,670 --> 00:28:09,670
'Tis a shame for a beautiful
woman like my Tae-Ran...

382
00:28:09,670 --> 00:28:11,090
...to waste her day in a workroom.

383
00:28:11,090 --> 00:28:12,690
The phone...

384
00:28:17,710 --> 00:28:18,790
Hello?

385
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:20,020
Hello, Guk-Hee.

386
00:28:20,030 --> 00:28:27,720
But it's very encouraging to see how you're using your talent to benefit...

387
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:29,000
...the movie industry.

388
00:28:31,120 --> 00:28:35,010
I'll bring some snacks
to cheer you up tonight.

389
00:28:37,110 --> 00:28:38,710
Bye.

390
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:48,840
Your wife wants you to come home
early to have dinner with your mom.

391
00:28:50,730 --> 00:28:52,690
Go home, your mom's waiting for you.

392
00:28:54,150 --> 00:28:55,970
Geez...

393
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:58,910
Geez...

394
00:29:09,840 --> 00:29:11,760
Myung-Pil...

395
00:29:14,140 --> 00:29:16,680
...let me give you some advice.

396
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:19,880
Stop it. Don't start.

397
00:29:23,940 --> 00:29:29,890
You should be thankful for
the wife who takes cares of you.

398
00:29:29,890 --> 00:29:33,830
You'll be punished if you
hurt a woman like that.

399
00:29:36,690 --> 00:29:41,100
Your wife's an acupuncturist,
and my wife is a housewife.

400
00:29:43,910 --> 00:29:45,880
Are you mocking me?

401
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,750
You always have one-night stands.

402
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:49,080
What a hypocrite.

403
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:54,830
I only do one-night stands,
but you're starting a relationship.

404
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:00,970
Do you think you can wreck your home?

405
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:04,130
I know a thing or two about you.

406
00:30:04,130 --> 00:30:06,850
You'll want more.

407
00:30:06,850 --> 00:30:08,700
That's why I'm giving you this advice.

408
00:30:11,130 --> 00:30:15,030
Just do one-night stands, like I do.

409
00:30:17,120 --> 00:30:18,150
Yes, Honey.

410
00:30:20,690 --> 00:30:22,770
Your mom's coming too.

411
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:25,050
Fine! Fine!

412
00:30:25,050 --> 00:30:26,730
I'm coming!

413
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:29,810
Why are you so irritated?

414
00:30:29,810 --> 00:30:31,040
Is it because of the house?

415
00:30:32,150 --> 00:30:34,930
Why do you want to have dinner today?

416
00:30:34,930 --> 00:30:36,790
Why tonight?

417
00:30:36,790 --> 00:30:38,950
You're the biggest
stumbling block in my life.

418
00:30:40,100 --> 00:30:42,690
Yes! I'm coming!

419
00:30:43,730 --> 00:30:45,690
Do you have a problem with that?

420
00:30:51,970 --> 00:30:52,990
Nam Jang-Mi?

421
00:30:52,990 --> 00:30:54,820
That divorcee came to the station?

422
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:55,830
Yes, Aunt.

423
00:30:55,830 --> 00:30:57,810
She's the woman I saw at the villa.

424
00:30:57,810 --> 00:30:59,700
Why was she at the police station?

425
00:31:00,740 --> 00:31:02,750
I don't know...

426
00:31:03,930 --> 00:31:05,870
Good evening!

427
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:07,970
I'm Min Seung-Gi,
a promising young officer.

428
00:31:08,910 --> 00:31:11,870
I found out why Nam Jang-Mi
was at the station!

429
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:17,940
She was a witness to the case transferred from the Sokcho station.

430
00:31:18,970 --> 00:31:20,040
Sokcho?

431
00:31:21,660 --> 00:31:23,680
They went to Sokcho?

432
00:31:25,700 --> 00:31:26,770
Bye.

433
00:31:34,970 --> 00:31:37,740
The food here tastes great, doesn't it?

434
00:31:38,980 --> 00:31:40,680
This is good.

435
00:31:42,700 --> 00:31:43,940
Myung-Pil, dig in.

436
00:31:43,950 --> 00:31:45,150
Okay.

437
00:31:45,150 --> 00:31:49,700
What happened to the house
was tough for me too...

438
00:31:49,700 --> 00:31:50,990
...but I'm sure we'll pull through.

439
00:31:50,990 --> 00:31:52,990
We've saved up a lot already.

440
00:31:52,990 --> 00:31:54,900
I'm sure we can save more.

441
00:32:01,700 --> 00:32:05,710
By the way, maybe I should work
at the market on Sundays too.

442
00:32:05,710 --> 00:32:07,690
They'll pay me twice as much
if I work on Sundays.

443
00:32:08,890 --> 00:32:12,140
Then... who's going to
baby-sit on Sundays?

444
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:16,890
You should let Myung-Pil
rest on Sundays.

445
00:32:16,890 --> 00:32:18,750
Don't make him baby-sit.

446
00:32:21,060 --> 00:32:24,140
What kind of a plan is that?

447
00:32:26,860 --> 00:32:31,780
Oh, the landlord said she's only going to increase our deposit by $30,000 more.

448
00:32:31,780 --> 00:32:34,010
She gave us a $7,000 discount.

449
00:32:34,010 --> 00:32:35,090
Good for you.

450
00:32:37,100 --> 00:32:38,810
Why don't we just drop the subject?

451
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:41,990
Let Myung-Pil eat in peace.

452
00:32:42,930 --> 00:32:45,860
You're right, let's not think about this.

453
00:32:45,860 --> 00:32:46,900
I'll work harder.

454
00:32:46,900 --> 00:32:49,070
We'll buy a house in 2 years.

455
00:32:49,990 --> 00:32:52,820
And when we do,
let's live together.

456
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:56,730
Sounds good.

457
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:00,680
Try some of this.

458
00:33:01,810 --> 00:33:03,100
Honey, eat.

459
00:33:13,010 --> 00:33:15,150
I need to use the restroom.

460
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:22,030
Jang-Mi?

461
00:33:22,030 --> 00:33:25,010
What? The Police called?

462
00:33:25,970 --> 00:33:27,910
