the pervert I saw at the beach.

464
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:37,700
I was there during the day too.

465
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:40,770
I don't want to go again.

466
00:33:42,010 --> 00:33:43,150
What should I do?

467
00:33:43,150 --> 00:33:44,950
I have to stay here.

468
00:33:45,850 --> 00:33:47,820
