what happened.

469
00:33:49,050 --> 00:33:51,660
Come to my place when you
get back from the station.

470
00:33:51,660 --> 00:33:53,000
Tell me what happened.

471
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:54,940
Bye.

472
00:34:07,020 --> 00:34:09,080
Hello? Hello?

473
00:34:11,810 --> 00:34:13,130
